        Lecture details contain the following parameters.
        Parameters:
        title: - lecture title
        date: - lecture date
        courseCode: - course code of the lecture
        view: - to decide whether to view the lecture selected or not
        profId: - enrolled professor's id
        link: - link of the lecture files
        details: - lecture details/content
        attendance: - attendance of the students who attended this lecture
